                "invention-title": [
                    "Modularized molten salt energy storage and ammonia cracking hydrogen production system",
                    "模块化熔盐储能裂解氨制氢系统"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a modularized molten salt energy storage ammonia cracking hydrogen production system which comprises a molten salt energy storage device, an ammonia decomposition device and an adsorption storage device. The fused salt energy storage device is used for converting electric energy into heat energy and storing the heat energy; the ammonia decomposition device is used for decomposing ammonia water into hydrogen and nitrogen; the adsorption and storage device is used for adsorbing and purifying reaction gas generated in the ammonia decomposition device and storing hydrogen; the fused salt energy storage device, the ammonia decomposition device and the adsorption storage device are sequentially connected through pipelines. The system integrates fused salt energy storage, heat exchange and ammonia cracking hydrogen production processes, the fused salt is used as an energy storage medium, valley electricity or wind electricity and photovoltaic abandoned electricity energy storage can be used for the ammonia cracking hydrogen production process, in the system operation process, the fused salt is used as the energy storage medium and a heat carrier, and the system has the advantages of being stable in operation parameter, high in hydrogen production efficiency, free of carbon dioxide emission, low in energy consumption and the like. And the operation cost economy is high."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种模块化熔盐储能裂解氨制氢系统，包括熔盐储能装置、氨分解装置以及吸附存储装置。所述熔盐储能装置用于将电能转化为热能并进行存储；所述氨分解装置用于将氨水分解为氢气和氮气；所述吸附存储装置用于吸附、提纯氨分解装置中生成的反应气体及存储氢气；所述熔盐储能装置、氨分解装置以及吸附存储装置依次通过管线连接。该系统集成了熔盐储能、换热与氨裂解制氢工艺，利用熔盐作为储能介质，可利用谷电或风电、光伏弃电储能用于裂解氨制氢过程，系统运行过程中，以熔盐作为储能介质及载热体，具有运行参数稳定、制氢效率高、无二氧化碳排放，运行成本经济性高的特点。"
                }
            ]
